| [1.5ct E-VVS1 IGI Ideal Lab](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28134308?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | IGI | $1,930 | 7.4mm | $1,287 | 10/10 — $20 less than the D-VVS1, same face-up, one color grade lower (still Colorless). Virtually identical visual result. The most efficient lab-grown 1.5ct on the catalog. |
