**Data insight:** The [1.5ct D-VVS1 lab at $1,950](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29219792?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is $1,280 cheaper than the natural 1ct G-VS2 at $3,230, yet delivers 16% more face-up diameter, higher color grade, and higher clarity grade. For buyers whose primary goal is maximum face-up visual impact per dollar, this is the most important data point in any 1ct engagement ring conversation.

